## Third-Party Licenses

This project includes code and dependencies from several open-source projects:

### Swiss Ephemeris
- **License**: Swiss Ephemeris Public License
- **Source**: https://www.astro.com/swisseph/
- **Usage**: Astronomical calculations and ephemeris data
- **Note**: Swiss Ephemeris is free for non-commercial use. Commercial use requires a license.

### React
- **License**: MIT License
- **Source**: https://github.com/facebook/react
- **Usage**: Frontend user interface framework

### Leaflet
- **License**: BSD 2-Clause License
- **Source**: https://github.com/Leaflet/Leaflet
- **Usage**: Interactive mapping functionality

### Flask
- **License**: BSD 3-Clause License
- **Source**: https://github.com/pallets/flask
- **Usage**: Backend web framework

### Vite
- **License**: MIT License
- **Source**: https://github.com/vitejs/vite
- **Usage**: Frontend build tool and development server

